# Title: Potential DLL Sideloading Via JsSchHlp
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-12-14
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading using JUSTSYSTEMS Japanese word processor
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_jsschhlp.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\JSESPR.dll" NOT ImageLoaded="C:\\Program Files\\Common Files\\Justsystem\\JsSchHlp\\*"